<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-0b83ce08-d410-4f35-a6d8-6c2bf4253bd0'>
            
<p class="">39.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-96aaa2e6-6165-4a6f-8655-e43899a68f2c">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-96aaa2e6-6165-4a6f-8655-e43899a68f2c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-96aaa2e6-6165-4a6f-8655-e43899a68f2c">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-96aaa2e6-6165-4a6f-8655-e43899a68f2c">
                Brigadier Low
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-96aaa2e6-6165-4a6f-8655-e43899a68f2c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-07-09/debates/5e5e28c9-63f3-4c83-84a1-daf73eda7a26/Greece(FamiliesOfPersonnel)#contribution-96aaa2e6-6165-4a6f-8655-e43899a68f2c">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Secretary of State for War whether wives of officers and men of the fighting services now serving in Greece are now entitled to join their husbands in Greece; if not, when such permission will be given; and whether <span id="220" class="column-number" data-column-number="220"></span> the same rules apply to British officers and men in the service of Military Government and U.N.R.R.A.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-96aaa2e6-6165-4a6f-8655-e43899a68f2c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-07-09/debates/5e5e28c9-63f3-4c83-84a1-daf73eda7a26/Greece(FamiliesOfPersonnel)#contribution-96aaa2e6-6165-4a6f-8655-e43899a68f2c">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-eeff0b8d-ff81-4130-8a5e-678a966590f6">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-eeff0b8d-ff81-4130-8a5e-678a966590f6">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-eeff0b8d-ff81-4130-8a5e-678a966590f6">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-eeff0b8d-ff81-4130-8a5e-678a966590f6">
                Mr. Bellenger
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-eeff0b8d-ff81-4130-8a5e-678a966590f6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-07-09/debates/5e5e28c9-63f3-4c83-84a1-daf73eda7a26/Greece(FamiliesOfPersonnel)#contribution-eeff0b8d-ff81-4130-8a5e-678a966590f6">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">My right hon. Friend dealt with the point raised in the first part of the Question on 4th June, in reply to Questions by the hon. Members for Hertford (Mr. Walker-Smith) and Westmorland (Mr. Vane). There is no British Military Government in Greece. Wives of U.N.R.R.A. personnel in Greece are allowed to join their husbands subject to the prior consent of the head of the Greek U.N.R.R.A. Mission and of the military authorities, and permission in these particular cases is not conditional on the husband remaining a further 12 months in Greece.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-eeff0b8d-ff81-4130-8a5e-678a966590f6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1946-07-09/debates/5e5e28c9-63f3-4c83-84a1-daf73eda7a26/Greece(FamiliesOfPersonnel)#contribution-eeff0b8d-ff81-4130-8a5e-678a966590f6">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-c8e63311-60de-490a-bf80-1648997d7a2d">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
